snippet.title: DUNK TANK into SCARY MYSTERY WATER!
snippet.description:
After Chad Wild Clay made "WHERE Are ALL These HACKERS COMING FROM?", Vy Qwaint created "IS JUSTIN REALLY the CLOAKER? The Truth Behind the Face Reveal using a Lie Detector Test", Daniel Gizmo uploaded "Regina QUIT YouTube for Tik Tok", and Melvin PZ9 filmed "Justin the Cloaker & Melvin PZ9 React to Spy Ninjas Greatest Battle Royale Fight Scenes", Chad, Vy, and Melvin figured out that agent Peters is recruiting hackers through a party bus! The bus led back to Regina who is playing Bella Poarch! And she won't stop doing Tik Toks! Before The Spy Ninjas deal with Project Zorgo, they have to do a Dunk Tank challenge, Tik Tok vs Youtube! They have to pull pranks, hit targets, copy ninja poses, attack Bob, and get dunked into something horrifying and dangerous in the Dunk Tank! Will they find out if Youtube or Tik Tok is better? Will the Spy Ninjas finally reunite to take down Agent Peters and Project Zorgo!? Thank you for watching my funny entertainment comedy adventure vlog videos in 2021!
